# Capability-ask v2 for the uppercase reference extension. Used
# by CapabilityAskIT's overwrite-on-reload sub-phase (I8): the
# fixture wasm on disk is swapped from the v1-embedded artifact
# to the v2-embedded artifact, the plugin's byte cache is
# invalidated via wf:cacheClear, and a second wf:call is expected
# to trigger recordAsk with these v2 triples — DELETEing the v1
# triples and INSERTing these.
#
# The v2 predicate set intentionally differs from v1 across
# every axis so the assertion after the reload distinguishes v1
# leftovers from v2 landings.

@prefix cap: <http://semantalytics.com/2021/03/ns/stardog/webfunction/capability#> .

<> a cap:CapabilityAsk ;
    cap:asksInterface cap:GraphCallbacks ;
    cap:asksMethod cap:GraphCallbacks_ExecuteQuery ;
    cap:asksHost "api.v2.example.com" ;
    cap:asksHttpPath "api.v2.example.com/read/" ;
    cap:asksRationale "Integration-test ask v2: overwrite-on-reload target — every axis differs from v1." .
